opkg-$name
===

The OSCAR project is a suite best practices free tools for clusters.

This package is generated by opkgc compiler from a distribution
independent description of the package.

====
opkg-api-$name
====

This package contains scripts used by OSCAR infrastructure to deploy,
and configure $name on cluster nodes.

====
opkg-server-$name
====

This package depends on needed software for $name to run on the server.

====
opkg-client-$name
====

This package depends on needed software for $name to run on the client nodes.

